QuestData.Title: A Crate of Sinvyr Ore
QuestData.Description: The crate is fairly big and looks heavy, but it also looks like something someone would be willing to compensate for. Take the crate to Gibbo at the Old Gate. He should be expecting the recurring shipment.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the crate to the Old Gate.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Gibbo at the Old Gate.
